0;\">조중현</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>6.공수표외주막는 우선협상자 지원자 신청</strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">http://bit.ly/2Kv2ip5</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">7.내가원하는 외주설정하기</span><br /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">http://bit.ly/372LkYT</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>8.심플한외주 소개서</strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">http://bit.ly/2qFjotp</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>9.스프린트 연구주제</strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">예시) 크로스플랫폼에 대한 프론티어분들의 경험치 습득</span><br /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">http://bit.ly/2NGSVV8</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '테크로드란', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '58-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-11-25 17:02:23', '2019-11-25 08:02:23', '', 58, 'https://community.techroad.io/archives/784', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
